{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The iPhone has revolutionized the lives of blind people with its incredible built-in VoiceOver technology — but can they use your app? A few simple steps can expand your user base within this growing community of iPhone users. In addition, adding accessibility to your app makes automating your UI testing much simpler. Discover how your app can be truly universal and simpler to test by adopting the iPhone Accessibility API."}],"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc10-122-accessibility-on-iphone-os"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC10","role":"sampleCode","title":"Accessibility on iPhone OS","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10-122-Accessibility-on-iPhone-OS","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2010\/122\/","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}},"references":{"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2010/122/":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2010\/122\/","checksum":null,"url":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/ww